abstract: A group of students form the Netherlands who are learning about the American election process are making campaign phone calls for a variety of candidates, including Rick Santorum and Ron Paul.
lead_paragraph: BEDFORD, N.H. -- Sake Slootweg, who was photographed outside Rick Santorum's campaign headquarters here, is part of a group of students from the Netherlands who are learning about the American election process and making campaign phone calls for a variety of candidates, including Mr. Santorum and Ron Paul.

headline.main: The Caucus Click: Dutch Get Out the Vote
